A shekara ta 1939, wata wuta ta halaka ginin, amma 'yan cocin Fada Johnson sun tsara yadda za a sake gina shi, kuma suka sake gina ginin da ƙarfe.
Fasto David Johnson, ɗan Uba Johnson kuma magajinsa a St. Martin's, ya kira wannan "abin dogara ga matalauta".
