Cromwell's Parliament Monument ya zama sabon abin tunawa da aka kai hari a cikin muhawara don sake rubuta tarihi
A cire shi zai zama horo mai kyau don irin lalacewar da Taliban ta yi a wasu abubuwa da yawa na al'adu da na addini a Ingila, waɗanda mabiyanta masu tsattsauran ra'ayi na Puritan suka yi.
Amma 'yan ƙungiyar Cromwell sun ce wannan ra'ayin Mr. Crick "wauta ne" kuma "ƙoƙari ne na sake rubuta tarihi".
John Goldsmith, shugaban Ƙungiyar Cromwell ya ce: Babu wata hanyar da za a iya cewa a wannan gardama ta cire mutum-mutumi, ba za a taɓa yin wani abu game da mutum-mutumi na Oliver Cromwell da ke fadar Westminster ba.
Cromwell bai yi aikin lalata al'adu da addini ba a lokacin yaƙin basasa na Ingila.
Wataƙila ana hukunta Cromwell ne don abin da kakansa Thomas ya yi, wanda ya rayu ƙarnuka da suka shige.
Yadda Sir William Hamo Thorneycroft ya kwatanta Cromwell da kyau ya nuna halin da ake da shi a ƙarni na 19 kuma ya nuna cewa an rubuta tarihin mutumin da mutane da yawa suka gaskata cewa yana da muhimmanci a tuna da shi.
Mista Goldsmith ya gaya wa jaridar The Sunday Telegraph: Mutane da yawa, musamman a ƙarni na 19 fiye da yanzu, sun ɗauki Cromwell a matsayin mai kāre majalisa daga zalunci a lokacin mulkinsa.
Ko wannan gaskiya ce ko a'a, ba a sani ba.
Abin da ya fi muhimmanci shi ne, rikici da aka yi a tsakiyar ƙarni na 17 ya kawo canji a ci gaban al'ummarmu, kuma ana ɗaukan Cromwell a matsayin ɗaya daga cikin mutanen da suka yi faɗa a wannan rikici.
Abin da ya cim ma a matsayin Ubangiji Mai Kāre ya cancanci a yi bikinsa kuma a tuna da shi.
Wani Alade Mai Ƙarfi Ya Kashe Manomi a Ƙasar Caina
Rahotanni sun nuna cewa wani manomi ne alade ya kai wa hari kuma ya kashe a wata kasuwa da ke kudu maso yammacin ƙasar Sin.
Jaridar Morning Post ta ruwaito a ranar Lahadi cewa an gano mutumin, wanda aka bayyana shi da Yuan, ya mutu kuma an rufe jijiyar zuciyarsa, a cikin wani kwarin jini kusa da wani gidan alade a kasuwar Liupanshui, lardin Guihou, a Kudancin China.
Wani manomi yana shirin yin wa aladu allurar rigakafi a gidansa a ranar 30 ga Mayu, 2005, a birnin Xining, lardin Qinghai, a ƙasar Caina.
An ba da rahoton cewa ya tafi da ɗan wansa daga lardin Yunnan da ke kusa a ranar Laraba don su sayar da aladu 15 a kasuwa.
Washegari, wani ɗan'uwansa ya iske shi ya mutu, kuma ya ga ƙofar gidan aladun da ke kusa da shi a buɗe.
Ya ce a cikin ramin akwai wani babban alade da yake zub da jini a bakinsa.
Rahoton ya ce, binciken da aka yi ya nuna cewa aladun da ya yi kiwon manomin ya yi nauyi mai nauyin kilo 249.5.
Wani ɗan'uwansa da ake kira Wu ya ce a jaridar Guiyang Evening New: Ƙafafun ɗan'uwansa suna cike da jini kuma suna da tsami.
Wani kyamarar tsaro ta kama Yuan yana shiga kasuwa da misalin karfe 4.40 na safiyar Alhamis don ciyar da aladun sa.
An gano gawarsa bayan awa ɗaya.
Wannan dabbar da ta kashe mutumin ba Yuan ba ce ko kuma ɗan'uwansa.
Manajan kasuwa ya gaya wa Evening News cewa an tsare aladun domin kada ya sake kai hari, yayin da 'yan sanda suke tattara shaida a wurin da abin ya faru.
An ba da rahoton cewa iyalin Yuan da kuma waɗanda suke kula da kasuwa suna taɗi don su yi ta'aziyya game da mutuwarsa.
Ko da yake ba a yawan samun irin wannan cutar ba, an taɓa samun rahotanni cewa aladu sun yi wa mutane hari a dā.
A shekara ta 2016, wani alade ya yi wa wata mata da mijinta barazana a gonarsu da ke jihar Massachusetts.
Shekara goma da ta shige, wani alade mai nauyin kilo 295 ya yi wa wani manomi ɗan Wales faɗa a cikin tarakta har sai da matarsa ta tsoratar da dabbar.
Bayan wani manomi da yake zama a jihar Oregon ya ji yunwa sa'ad da aladu suka ci shi a shekara ta 2012, wani manomi a jihar Manitoba ya gaya wa gidan rediyon CBC cewa ba safai aladu suke cin naman daji ba, amma idan suka ɗanɗana jini, hakan zai sa su yi fushi.
Ya ce: Suna son su yi wasa.
Suna son su san abubuwa kamar yara, ba sa son su yi maka lahani.
Yana da muhimmanci ka yi musu biyayya.
