An yi maraba da Erdogan a hanyoyi dabam dabam a Cologne
A ranar Asabar (29 ga Satumba), sa'ad da shugabannin Turkiya da Jamus suka taru don cin abinci a birnin Berlin, ana sanyaya iska kuma sama ya yi blue.
Ranar ƙarshe ce ta ziyarar Shugaba Erdogan a Jamus - da nufin sake gina dangantaka tsakanin ƙasashen NATO.
Ba su yarda ba game da wasu batutuwa da suka shafi 'yancin 'yan Adam, 'yancin 'yan jarida, da kuma kasancewa cikin Tarayyar Turai.
Sai Erdogan ya tafi Cologne don ya buɗe sabon babban masallaci.
Wannan birni ne ke da yawan mutanen Turkiya a wajen ƙasar.
'Yan sanda sun ce sun hana mutane 25,000 su taru a masallacin, amma mutane da yawa sun zo don su ga shugaban ƙasar.
Daruruwan 'yan adawa da Erdogan - da yawa daga cikin Kurdawa ne - sun yi magana, suna yaba wa dabarun Erdogan da kuma shawarar da gwamnatin Jamus ta yanke na ba shi mafaka.
Masu zanga-zangar da ke ɓangarorin biyu sun nuna ƙarfin hali na baƙo da Turkawa na Jamus suka yaba masa a matsayin gwarzo amma wasu suka ɗauke shi a matsayin mai zalunci.
