Trump ya ce Kavanaugh 'ya sha wahala daga mummunan hali, fushi' na Jam'iyyar Democrat
"Zaɓe wa Alƙali Kavanaugh zaɓe ne na ƙin al'adun Jam'iyyar Democrat", in ji Trump a wani taro na jam'iyyar a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Trump ya ce tun lokacin da aka naɗa Kavanaugh, "ya sha wahala daga mugunta, fushi" na Jam'iyyar Democrat.
Kavanaugh ya shaida a gaban Majalisa a ranar Alhamis, ya musanta zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin Christine Blasey Ford a shekarun baya lokacin da take matashiya.
Ford ya ba da shaida a kan zargin da ya yi a wannan shari'ar.
