Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara yakin neman zabensa a daren yau a Wheeling, West Virginia
Wannan ne tafiyar farko cikin biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, har da zuwa wurare masu kyau a kusa da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Game da kuri'ar tabbatar da zaben da aka dakatar na wani lokaci domin cike gibin da aka samu a Kotun Koli, Trump ya yi niyyar samun goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe a tsakiyar shekara yayin da 'yan Republican ke gab da rasa majalisar dokoki a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne ake kallon hoton Trump a yammacin Virginia?
An shirya za a fara wasan Trump Wheeling a yammacin Virginia da karfe 7 na yamma, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018
Za ka iya kallon hoton Trump na West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye a YouTube.
Trump na iya yin jawabi a Kotun Koli a wannan makon a lokacin sauraron shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai tashin hankali yayin da ake gabatar da tuhume-tuhume na fyade saboda dakatar da kuri'ar nadin na makonni biyu don binciken FBI
Amma wannan jerin ayyukan na taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar kalubale a zaben Nuwamba su inganta matsayinsu
A sakamakon haka, wannan kamfen na neman masu jefa kuri'a ya ce wadannan 'yan wasan biyar na mako mai zuwa suna da niyyar "sarrafa masu sa kai da masu tallafawa a lokacin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
Gudanar da majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga manufofinsa, don haka shugaban ya je wurare da dama da zai iya zuwa lokacin da aka shiga lokacin zaɓe,  wani mai magana da yawun kamfen na Trump da ya ƙi bayyana sunansa ya gaya wa Reuters
An shirya wasan da za a yi a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling, ana iya samun masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania a wannan maraice kuma za a nuna shi a kan kafofin watsa labarai a Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata, wannan shine karo na farko da ya samu nasara sama da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016
