HIV/AIDS a China ya ba da rahoton ƙaruwar kashi 14% a sababbin masu cutar
China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar kashi 14% na yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da Aids.
Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne ke cikin wannan yanayin a ƙasar, in ji ma'aikatan lafiya.
Akalla mutane 40,000 ne aka yi wa shari'a a kashi na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kaɗai.
Yawancin sababbin shari'o'in cututtuka ne na jima'i, wannan yana kawo canji idan aka kwatanta da na baya.
A wasu wurare a ƙasar Sin, cutar HIV tana yaduwa da sauri domin jini da ke ɗauke da cutar.
Amma adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar ta wannan hanyar ya ragu kuma ya kusan ƙaru, in ji ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Kowace shekara, duk da haka, adadin mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da Aids a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i abu ne mai tsanani a tsakanin mutanen da suke yin jima'i da ke nuna bambancin jinsi.
An ba da izinin luwaɗi a ƙasar Caina a shekara ta 1997, amma an ci gaba da nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi
Domin yawan al'adu da suka zama ruwan dare, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna aure.
Yawancin cututtuka na wannan cuta suna faruwa ne domin rashin kāriya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin ƙasar Sin ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta ba kowa magani don cutar HIV.
Maxine Waters ta yi jayayya cewa aikin ya ba da bayani ga 'yan majalisa na GOP, yana nuna ƙarya da kuma rikici
A ranar Asabar, wakilin majalisar wakilai na Amirka, Maxine Waters, ya musanta zargin da ake yi cewa wani a cikin ma'aikatansa ya saka bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisa uku na jam'iyyar Republican a shafukan Wikipedia.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Democrat a Los Angeles ya yi magana da tabbaci cewa masu bincike da shafukan yanar gizo na 'yan adawa ne ke yin irin wannan jawabin.
Waters ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter: Wannan ƙarya ce, ƙarya ce mai zurfi.
An ce bayanin da aka bayar ya haɗa da adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattijai na Amirka Lindsey Graham daga South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka daga Utah.
Wannan bayanin ya bayyana a ranar Alhamis a intanet, wanda wani mai ba da labari a kan Capitol Hill ya aika a lokacin da Majalisar Dattawa ke sauraron shari'ar babban alkalin Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da cin zarafin mata.
An ba da wannan bayanin ne bayan da 'yan majalisa uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Jaridar The Hill ta ba da rahoton cewa wasu shafukan yanar gizo na masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP da ke nuna asalin wanda ya aika bayanin ya nuna ofishin Waters kuma ya cire bayanin aiki tare da Waters.
Waters ya ci gaba: "Waɗannan maganganun ƙarya ne, ƙarya ce ta gaske".
"Abokin aikina - wanda aka fallasa sunansa, bayanansa, da kuma kāriyarsa saboda wannan zamba da kuma maganganun - ba zai taɓa ba da irin wannan bayanin ba.
Waɗannan maganganun banza ƙarya ne, ƙarya ce ta banza".
Nan da nan, mutane da suka haɗa da tsohon sakataren labarai na fadar White House, Ari Fleischer, suka yi ba'a game da jawabin Waters a Intane.
Fleischer ya rubuta: Yadda ta ƙi ya nuna cewa tana fushi ne.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba shi da zuciyar zama ɗan majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da wani abin da bai yi ba, ba shi da dalilin yin fushi.
Ba sa son su zama masu taurin kai.
Bai kamata su yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa mai zargin yake tuhumarsu ba.
Ya kamata su kasance da kwanciyar hankali".
Da alama Fleischer yana kwatanta yadda Waters ya amsa da abin da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat suka ce game da Alƙali Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukarsa suka ce ya yi fushi sosai a shari'ar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman kujerar Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, shi ma ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
Ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter: "Wannan labari ne mai tsanani idan gaskiya ne".
A jawabinsa, Water ya ce ofishinsa ya sanar da masu kula da shari'a da kuma hukuma game da waɗannan ƙaryace-ƙaryacen.
Ya ci gaba: "Za mu tabbata cewa an fallasa waɗannan masu ta da hankali, kuma za a hukunta su don ayyukansu na lalata da kuma sa kowa cikin abokan aikina cikin haɗari".
Abokan Johnny English sun sake yin faɗa - fim ɗin Rowan Atkinson
A yanzu haka ya zama ruwan dare a ga muhimmancin Brexit a kowane sabon fim daga ra'ayin Birtaniya kuma ya zama daidai da sake farfado da fim din Johnny English - wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake farfadowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Shin waɗannan maganganun da ake yi game da rashin hankali za su zama sabon abu ne ga ƙasashen waje?
Duk da haka, Johnny English, ɗan fim mai suna The Dark Knight, ya sami lasisinsa na biyu da ya ba da mamaki - sunan da ya nuna cewa yana wasa da siffar da ba a yi wa masu son fina-finai ba da ba Turanci ba.
Wannan shi ne babban dan wasan da duk da cewa yana da sha'awar shahara, ya yi rawar Clouseau, Mr Bean da kuma dan wasan da ya yi waka a waƙar Chariots of Fire a London a bikin bude gasar Olympics ta 2012.
Da farko kuma, ya yi kwaikwayon Atkinson, wani matafiyi da ya yi tafiya a ƙasashen waje, wanda aka nuna a cikin tallace-tallace na Barclaycard da aka manta da su a talabijin, kuma ya bar matsaloli a baya.
Akwai abu ɗaya ko biyu da ya dace da ni a kwanan nan.
Ina son Johnny English da yake zuwa jirgi mai saukar ungulu da rigar soja da kuma takunkumin da ke kan kansa.
An nuna Atkinson da baiwar yin ba'a, amma abin dariya ba shi da ban dariya kuma ba dole ba ne, musamman ma tun da irin fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible yanzu suna nuna ba'a a matsayin abu mai muhimmanci.
Kamar dai an shirya wasan kwaikwayo ne don yara ba manya ba, kuma a ganina wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English ba ya nuna fasaha da kuma sha'awar kamar fina-finai marasa sauti na Atkinson tare da mutuntaka Bean.
Ruwan da ke zubowa daga ƙasa ya nuna cewa ƙasar Biritaniya tana cikin matsala sosai.
Kwamfuta mai suna Hackers ta ɓoye asirin leƙen asirin Birtaniya, ta bayyana sunayen dukan leƙen asirin Birtaniya da ke aiki, abin da ya ba da mamaki ga leƙen asirin da ke aiki - abin baƙin ciki Kevin Eldon yana da ɗan aiki.
Ka yi la'akari da firaministan da ke ɗaukaka kansa a matsayin mai neman zaɓen da kuma mai gwagwarmaya, amma kuma ya zama abin ƙyama a siyasa: Emma Thompson tana ƙoƙari ta yi koyi da halin kirki na Teresa-May amma ba za a iya rubuta kome game da ita ba.
Masu ba shi shawara sun yi masa kashedi cewa tun da yake ba su da sauran 'yan leƙen asiri, zai ɗauki wanda ya yi ritaya.
Kuma wannan yana nufin cewa Johnny English mai ban mamaki, wanda yanzu an ɗauke shi aiki a matsayin shugaban makarantar sakandare, amma yana koyarwa ba tare da rikodin ba shine hanyar ɓoyewa: fina-finai masu ban sha'awa a nan kamar yadda Turanci ya yi alkawarin makarantar makarantar Rock.
An kai English Whitehall da sauri don taron gaggawa kuma ya haɗu da tsohon abokin hamayyarsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya yi.
Yanzu da yake Bough ya yi aure, an ɗaure shi ga kyaftin jirgin ruwa mai saukar ungulu, wanda Vicki Pepperdine take ɓata lokaci a matsayin yarinya mai saurin fushi.
Saboda haka, Batman da Robin da suka saba yin kuskure a cikin Sashen 'Yan Sanda sun dawo da ƙarfi, suna haɗuwa da Ophelia Bulletova mai kyau Olga Kurylenko.
Sa'ad da firaministan ya faɗa cikin tarkon wani mai fasaha mai arziki, mai ba da labari, wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Britaniya: Jason Volta mai ba da labari, Jake Lacy ne ya yi wasa.
English da Bough sun fara tafiya mai ban dariya, suna yin kamar masu kula da gida, suna cin wuta a gidan cin abinci na Faransa; sun fara aikata laifi kuma sun shiga cikin jirgin Volta mai ban mamaki; kuma English ya fara rikici lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da na'urar Virtual Reality don sanin abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Duk da haka, an daina hutu domin wannan abin da ya faru, amma duk da haka, akwai talabijin na yara a cikin dukan wannan.
Hakika, ba haka yake ba.
Bayan na kalli wasu fina-finai na Johnny English, sai na soma tunani: Shin masana'antar fim na ƙasar Biritaniya suna ba Rowan Atkinson aikin da ya dace da baiwarsa?
Ƙungiyoyin ma'aikata sun ƙi amincewa da shirin da aka yi na biya ma'aikata kwanaki biyar a rana a ƙasar Britaniya
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi nazari a kan wata babbar manufa da za ta sa 'yan Britaniya su yi aiki na kwana huɗu a mako - amma a biya su kwana biyar.
An ba da rahoton cewa wannan rukunin suna son manajojin kamfanoni su ba ma'aikata ƙarin hutu don su samu kuɗin da suka samu daga yin amfani da fasahar kere-kere.
Hakan zai sa ma'aikatan su yi hutu na kwana uku a ƙarshen mako, amma a biya su wata rana.
Waɗannan majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai "dace" da manufar jam'iyyar ta tattalin arziki da kuma manufar gyara ƙasar don amfanin ma'aikata.
Majalisar Ƙungiyoyin Ƙwadago ta amince da yin aiki kwana huɗu a mako don ma'aikata su amfana daga canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani sanannen majiyar Jam'iyyar Labour ya gaya wa jaridar The Sunday Times: 'Ana sa ran za a sanar da canjin manufofin kafin ƙarshen wannan bazarar.
'Wannan ba zai faru ba da dare ba amma yin aiki kwana huɗu a mako muradi ne da ya jitu da tsarin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arzikin ƙasa don amfanin aiki da kuma tsarin masana'antu na jam'iyyar.'
Jam'iyyar Labour ba za ta kasance ta farko da ta amince da irin wannan shawarar ba, kamar yadda Jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin a lokacin zaben kasa na 2017 don yin aiki kwana hudu a mako.
Amma, a yanzu jam'iyyar Labour ba ta amince da wannan muradin ba.
Wani kakakin Jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: 'Ba manufar jam'iyyar ba ce a yi aiki kwana huɗu a mako, kuma ba batun da jam'iyyar take tattaunawa ba ne.'
Shugaban jam'iyyar Shadow John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour na makon da ya gabata don ya bincika ra'ayinsa game da canjin tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce yana son ya kawar da 'masu mulki marasa mutunci' da kuma 'masu son kai' daga kamfanoni.
Shadow Chancellor's plans kuma ya ce masu hannun jari na yanzu a kamfanonin ruwa ba za su iya samun duk kuɗin da suka samu ba domin gwamnatin Labour za ta 'cire kuɗin' saboda kuskuren da ake zaton an yi.
Ya kuma ba da shawarar a saka ma'aikata a kan kwamitocin kamfanoni kuma a kafa Asusun Tattalin Arziki don a ba ma'aikata kashi 10 cikin ɗari na hannun jari na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu, waɗanda za su iya samun riba na shekara-shekara har zuwa fam 500.
Lindsey Graham, John Kennedy sun gaya wa "60 Minutes" ko binciken FBI game da Kavanaugh zai iya canja ra'ayinsu
Binciken FBI game da zargin da aka yi wa Alkalin Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta kuri'ar ƙarshe na zaɓen da aka yi masa a Kotun Koli da akalla kashi bakwai, wanda ya sa mutane suka yi tambaya ko binciken da kotun ta yi zai sa wasu 'yan Republican su ƙi goyon bayanta.
A wata hira da aka yi da 'yan majalisa a ranar Lahadi, Scott Pelley, ɗan jaridar "60 Minutes" ya tambayi 'yan majalisa na Republican, John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko FBI za ta iya ba da wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Wani abokin aikinsa daga South Carolina ne ya haifi Kennedy.
"Ina nufin, na ji", in ji Kennedy.
"Sa'ad da na je shari'ar, na ce ina magana da Alƙali Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan haka, na ce, 'Ka yi wannan abin?'
Ya yi ta ƙwanƙwasawa, yana cizon haƙora, ba ya kuwa raba tumaki da tumaki".
Amma, an ga cewa ba za a iya canja zaɓen Graham ba.
Ya ce: "Na yanke shawara game da Brett Kavanaugh kuma za a bukaci wani babban hukunci don a canja shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san wannan: Brett ya ƙi yaƙi", in ji Graham, yana nuni ga Christine Blasey Ford.
"Ba wanda zai iya tabbatar da hakan.
Shekaru 36 sun shige.
Na ga wani sabon abu da zai iya canja".
Mene ne Bikin Ƙasar Duniya, Kuma Shin Ya Yi Wani Abu don Ya Ƙarfafa Talauci?
A wannan Asabar New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na kiɗa na bazara wanda ke nuna manyan masu kiɗa na gaske kuma yana da manufa mai ban sha'awa: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai tara dubban mutane a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park ba kawai don jin daɗin waƙoƙin Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don wayar da kan mutane game da ainihin manufar kawar da talauci a 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke daukar mataki don magance ta.
Don a samu tikitin zuwa wurin (sai dai idan mutum yana son ya biya kuɗin tikitin VIP), waɗanda suka halarci liyafar suna bukatar su yi wasu ayyuka, kamar su ba da kansu, aika saƙon imel zuwa ga shugabannin duniya, yin waya, ko kuma su yi wani abu da zai taimaka wajen sanar da mutane game da aikin kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya Global Citizen ta cim ma burinta da yake shekara 12 kawai ta rage?
Shin ba da tikitin kyauta don liyafa hanya ce mai kyau na sa mutane su yi wani abu, ko kuma wata hanya ce ta "ƙara ƙaruwa" - mutane suna ganin cewa suna kawo canji ta wajen yin amfani da dandalin sada zumunta ko kuma aika saƙo a dandalin Twitter?
A shekara ta 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta rubuta abubuwa fiye da miliyan 19 da masu goyon bayanta suka yi don su cim ma maƙasudai dabam-dabam.
Ya ce waɗannan matakan sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su yi alkawarin kuɗin da za su kashe wajen dala biliyan 37 don su shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta amince da alkawura 390 da sanarwa sakamakon matakan da ta ɗauka, aƙalla an amince da ko an biya dala biliyan 10 daga asusun.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa har zuwa yanzu, an ba da kuɗi da ya shafi rayukan mutane miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Wasu manyan masu ba da gudummawa sun kafa The Power of Nutrition, ƙungiyar masu saka hannun jari ta Burtaniya da ke da alhakin "taimaka wa yara su haɓaka har sai sun sami damar yin amfani da baiwarsu gaba ɗaya", suna ba da shawarar ba Rwanda dala miliyan 35 don magance matsalar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a ƙasar bayan sun karɓi saƙonni sama da 4,700 daga Twitter daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Birtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasashe da kuma 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya kawo ƙarshen rashin adalci a cikin al'umma saboda rashin abinci mai gina jiki", in ji wakilin The Power of Nutrition Tracey Ullman ga masu sauraro a wani wasan kwaikwayo da aka gudanar a Landan a watan Afrilu 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan da aka ɗauki matakai fiye da 5,000 a ƙasar Ingila don a inganta abinci mai gina jiki na mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da wani asusu don aikin nan, Power Nutrition, wanda zai ceci mata da yara miliyan 5 daga rashin abinci mai gina jiki.
A wani talifi da aka saka a dandalinsa, an yi wannan tambayar: "Me ya sa kuke ganin cewa za mu iya kawar da yunwa?"
Global citizen ta ce: "Zai zama doguwar tafiya mai wuya - a wasu lokatai za mu yi tuntuɓe kuma mu faɗi.
Amma kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin kare haƙƙin ɗan adam da kuma adawa da mulkin kama karya da suka riga mu, za mu yi nasara, domin ƙarfi haɗin kai ne.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe suna cikin mawaƙa da za su yi biki a bikin bazara na New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gudanar.
{Asar Amirka za ta iya amfani da Sojojin Ruwa don "ƙuntata" kayayyakin da Rasha ke fitarwa na makamashi - Ministan Harkokin Cikin Gida
Idan ya cancanta gwamnatin Amurka za ta yi amfani da Sojojin Ruwa don hana makamashin Rasha zuwa kasuwanni, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, wanda Washington Examiner ta nakalto.
Zinke ya ce, Rasha ta shiga yaƙin Siriya - inda ta tura sojoji daga gwamnatin da ke mulki - domin neman sababbin kasuwanni na makamashi ne kawai.
An ba da rahoton cewa ya ce: "Na yi imani cewa dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne don su sayar da makamashi kamar yadda suka yi a gabashin Turai, a kudancin Turai".
Amma, in ji wannan ma'aikacin gwamnati, akwai hanyoyin da za a magance wannan.
Ya ce: "Amurka tana da ikon yin amfani da Sojojin Ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin teku suna buɗe, kuma idan ya cancanta, don hana makamashi daga zuwa kasuwa.
Zinke yana magana ne a taron da wata ƙungiya mai suna Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata ƙungiya da ba ta neman riba ba ce da ta ce ita ce "mai ba da shawara ga masu amfani da makamashi" a Amirka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta yadda gwamnatin Amirka ta bi da Rasha da Iran, yana cewa suna da irin wannan nasara.
"Domin tattalin arziki Iran da Rasha za su iya zaɓan su yi amfani da wannan hanyar kuma su canja mai", in ji shi, yana kwatanta Rasha a matsayin "wani ƙaramin gari" da tattalin arzikinta ya dogara ne da man fetur.
Wannan jawabin ya zo ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke shirin kara yawan isar da iskar gas da aka yi a Turai, wanda zai fitar da Rasha, wadda ke sayar da ƙarfe ga masu sayen Turai.
Saboda haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, har da Shugaban Amirka Donald Trump da kansa, suna ƙoƙarin su sa Jamus ta daina aikin "Nord Stream 2" wanda ba daidai ba ne, wanda a cewar Trump, ya sa Moscow ta sake mallakar Berlin.
Moscow ta ci gaba da cewa bututun mai mai na Nord Stream 2 da aka kashe dala biliyan 11, wanda nufinsa shi ne ya ƙara ƙarfinsa zuwa wajen wajen kilomita biliyan 110, aikin kasuwanci ne kawai.
Gwamnatin Rasha ta nace cewa ƙin da Gwamnatin Amirka ta yi wa aikin na siyasa ne kawai kuma misali ne na gasa da ba ta dace ba.
"Na yi imani mun yarda cewa makamashi ba makami ne na zalunci ba kuma masu amfani suna da 'yancin zaɓar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Amma, a yanzu, Amirka ta yi watsi da wannan shawarar, domin Jamus ta ce za ta ci gaba da tallafa wa aikin.
Ƙungiyar masana'antun Jamus mai suna Federation of German Industries (BDI) ta ce Amirka ta daina bin dokokin da ƙungiyar Tarayyar Turai ta kafa game da makamashi da kuma yarjejeniyar da gwamnatin Jamus da Rasha suka yi.
"Ina damuwa sosai idan wata ƙasa ta yi amfani da makamashi a cikin mu", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban Ƙungiyar Masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin Shugabar Jamus Angela Merkel da Shugaba Vladimir Putin na Rasha.
Elizabeth Warren Za Ta Yi Tunanin Taron Shugaban Kasa A Shekarar 2020, In Ji Wani Sanatan Massachusetts
Elizabeth Warren, wata 'yar majalisar dattijai daga Massachusetts, ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi tunani sosai game da neman shugaban kasa bayan zaɓen tsakiyar shekara.
A majami'ar birnin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar cewa zai yi tunanin yin murabus.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su kama mulki a Washington kuma su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, wadda mace take shugabanta", in ji The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da neman shugabancin ƙasar".
Warren ya yi wa Shugaba Donald Trump ba'a a zauren gari, yana cewa yana barin ƙasar.
Ya ce, "Ina damuwa sosai game da abin da Donald Trump yake yi da dimokiradiyarmu".
Warren ya fallasa Trump a fili da kuma wanda ya naɗa a Kotun Koli, wato, Brett Kavanaugh.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter, "a zahiri ana bukatar binciken FBI kafin mu kada kuri'a".
Duk da haka, wani binciken da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin mazauna mazabar Warren ba su tsammanin ya kamata ya tsaya takara a 2020.
Bisa ga wani bincike da Cibiyar Bincike a Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk da Boston Globe suka yi, kashi 58 cikin ɗari na waɗanda suke da 'yancin kada kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce ɗan majalisar ba zai yi takara ba.
Kashi 32 cikin ɗari sun amince da shi ya yi murabus.
Wani bincike ya nuna cewa mutane da yawa sun goyi bayan tsohon Gwamna Deval Patrick, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce ya yi zaɓen kansa, amma kashi 48 sun ce ba zai yi ba.
Wasu fitattun 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat da aka ce za su yi takara a zaben 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da dan majalisar dattijai na Vermont Bernie Sanders.
Biden ya ce zai yanke hukunci a watan Janairu, a cewar wani rahoto na Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta yi magana game da ciwon tsoro na Track Palin (PTSD) a taron jam'iyyar Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya yi bazara a Iraki bayan an tura shi aiki a watan Satumba.
An kama shi kuma an zarge shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mata a gida a daren Litinin
"Abin da ya faru da ɗana, abin da ya faru da shi bayan ya dawo, yana kama da sakamakon PTSD da wasu iyalai ke fuskanta kuma sojojinmu sun dawo da rauni", in ji shi ga masu sauraro a wani taron jam'iyyar Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta ce, "ba a son a yi magana game da wannan batun" kuma ta ce ɗanta da kuma wasu tsoffin sojoji "suna dawowa da bambanci, suna dawowa da gaba gaɗi, suna mamaki ko akwai daraja ga abin da wasu sojoji da sojojin sama da kuma kowane soja ya yi wa ƙasarsu".
An kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da cin zarafin mace a cikin gida, shiga cikin rahoton tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma riƙe da makami yayin da ya sha, in ji Dan Bennett, lauya na Ma'aikatar 'Yan Sanda ta Wasilla.
Kasashe 18 a D.C. sun goyi bayan ƙalubalan da aka yi wa sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 na Amirka da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan ƙalubalen doka na sabuwar manufar Amirka na hana waɗanda ake zalunta da ƙungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda ko kuma waɗanda ake zaluntarsu a gida samun mafaka.
Wakilan ƙasashe 18 da kuma yankuna na Amirka sun yi jawabi a kan waɗanda wannan dokar ta shafa a ranar Jumma'a a Washington don su goyi bayan wani mai neman mafaka da ya ƙalubalanci wannan dokar, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai ƙara a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da Ƙungiyar 'Yancin 'Yan Adam ta Amirka ta gabatar a watan Agusta game da tsarin gwamnati ba.
Ya ce matarsa "da 'ya'yan 'yan tawagarsa" sun wulakanta shi amma jami'an gwamnatin Amirka sun ƙi amincewa da bukatarsa ta mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare shi a kurkuku a Texas.
Hukumomin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun ce El Salvador da Honduras da kuma Guatemala ne ƙasashen da suka fi yawan masu neman mafaka a Amirka, domin waɗannan ƙasashen suna fama da matsalolin 'yan bindiga da kuma nuna ƙarfi a gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka a Amurka ta sauya hukuncin da Hukumar Kula da Shige da Fice ta yanke a shekara ta 2014 wanda ya ba 'yan gudun hijira da ba su da takardun da za su tsere daga cin zarafin gida damar neman mafaka.
Babban Lauyan Gundumar Columbia Karl Racine ya ce a ranar Jumma'a cewa sabuwar dokar "ta saɓa wa dokar ƙasa, ta tarayya [ta Amirka] da kuma ta duniya".
"Dokar Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya ta bukaci a bincika dukan buƙatun mafaka bisa ga gaskiya da kuma yanayin kowane buƙata, kuma wannan ƙuntatawa ya saɓa wa wannan muhimmin batu", in ji rahoton da wata ƙungiyar da manufofin suka shafa.
Ƙari ga haka, masu ba da shawara sun ce hana 'yan gudun hijira shiga ƙasar Amirka zai iya sa tattalin arziki ya yi sanyi, kuma hakan zai sa su soma kasuwanci ko kuma su samu "aiki mai kyau".
Babban Lauyan Jeff Sessions ya umurci jami'an kula da 'yan gudun hijira da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke tsere wa cin zarafin gida ko kuma ƙungiyoyin masu aikata laifi a watan Yuni.
"Ana samun mafaka ga waɗanda suka gudu daga ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoron launin fata, addini, ƙasa ko kasancewa cikin wani rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a ranar 11 ga Yuni lokacin da ya sanar da manufar.
Ba a yi nufin mafaka ta magance dukan matsaloli ba - har ma da matsaloli masu tsanani da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a dukan duniya.
