Michael Vann, ɗan shekara 72, ya ce, "Ba zan taɓa yin hakan ba, amma hakan yana sa ni ji kamar na yi kasala".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dokta James Vann, sun je suka dasa furanni bayan wannan gangamin, wanda ƙungiyar mawaƙa ta matasa ta Brentwood Imperial suka yi ja-gora.
Michael Vann ya ce "ya ji ya sami girma sosai da ya sa hannu a wannan zanga-zangar" kuma ya daɗa cewa "ƙarfin hali na mayaƙi na gaske yana nuna goyon bayan da jama'a suka nuna".
Masu son wasan MMA sun yi daddare suna kallon Bellator 206, amma sai aka nuna musu Peppa Pig
Ka yi tunanin cewa ka yi dare kana kallon Bellator 206 da ke cike da mutane amma ba ka ga abin da ya faru ba.
A jerin daga San Jose, an nuna faɗace-faɗace guda 13, a cikin labarai shida da aka nuna a babban katin kuma an watsa su kai tsaye a dukan dare a Channel 5 a Birtaniya.
Da ƙarfe shida na safe, sa'ad da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald suke shirin yin wa juna murna, sai ɗan ƙasar Birtaniya ya bar shi da ɗan adam a cikin dutse mai daraja sa'ad da aka canja shirin zuwa Peppa Pig.
Wasu sun yi baƙin ciki cewa sun yi barci har dare don su kalli yadda ake faɗa.
Wani mai amfani da shafin Twitter ya kwatanta canja wurin watsa shirye-shiryen zuwa jaridu na yara a matsayin "wasa".
"Dokar gwamnati ce cewa ba za a iya yin wasan a ƙarfe shida na safe ba, saboda haka, dole ne su yi wasan yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, babban mataimakin shugaban kasuwanci da sadarwa na Bellator, sa'ad da aka tambaye shi dalilin canja shirin.
"Ka yi wa naman alade kaza, ko ba haka ba?"
Shugaban kamfanin Bellator Scott Coker ya ce za su yi aiki da nasu tsarin don ya haɗa da 'yan ƙasar Birtaniya a nan gaba.
Coker ya ce: "Ina ganin idan na sake yin wannan wasan, wataƙila za a iya yin wani abu.
"Amma yanzu ƙarfe shida na safe ne a ranar Lahadi, kuma ba za mu iya yin kome ba sai ranar Lahadi da muke da lokaci, ranar Litinin ce a gare su.
Amma muna ci gaba da yin hakan.
A gaskiya, idan na kashe wayar, sai in aika musu da saƙonni da yawa kuma dukansu suna da lahani.
Muna ƙoƙarin gyara abubuwa, muna ganin cewa matsalar fasaha ce.
Amma, ba haka batun yake ba.
Ina son in tabbatar maka cewa hakan ba zai sake faruwa ba.
Za mu yi faɗa biyar maimakon shida - kamar yadda muka saba - muna ƙoƙari mu yi faɗa don mu ci nasara amma muna ƙara gishiri.
Muna baƙin ciki sosai don abin da ya faru".
Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya yi wa kansa wariya domin jinsi
Wannan ɗan wasa mai tsere na Olympics, Tom Daley, ya yi wa kansa lahani domin jinsi - amma hakan ya motsa shi ya yi nasara.
Wannan saurayi mai zunubi 24 ya ce bai fahimci cewa "ba kowa ba ne kamar ni" ba sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare.
A jawabinsa na farko a Radio 4 Desert Island Discs a matsayin Lauren Laverne, ya yi magana game da 'yancin 'yan luwadi don ya ba wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce, kasancewa iyaye ya sa ba ma damuwa da samun lambar yabo a gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, wadda ta saba gabatar da shirin, ta yi watanni da yawa ba ta aiki don rashin lafiya.
Da yake ya fito a matsayin wanda aka ƙi a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce ya ji "ƙanƙantacce" a lokacin da yake girma domin "ba a yarda a yi sha'awar yara maza da mata a cikin al'umma ba".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, wannan halin tawali'u da kuma bambancin da nake da shi ya taimaka mini sosai in yi nasara".
Ta so ta nuna cewa ita "wani abu ce" don kada ta yanke wa kowa shawara sa'ad da aka gano inda ta fito.
Wanda ya lashe lambar tagulla sau biyu a gasar Olympics babban mai fafutukar kare hakkin 'yan luwadi ne kuma ya yi amfani da kasancewarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan bazarar a Ostareliya don yin kira ga ƙarin ƙasashe da su daina nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi hakan ne don yana ganin cewa yana da gatan yin rayuwa a hanyar da ba ta da wata matsala kuma yana son ya ba wasu "bege".
Gwarzon zakara na duniya sau uku ya ce ya yi soyayya da wani mutum - mai shirya fina-finai na Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a 2013 - "ya sa ni baƙin ciki".
Daley ta auri wani wanda ya lashe kyautar Oscar, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20 a bara, amma ta ce shekarun ba matsala ba ne.
"Idan ka fuskanci matsaloli da yawa a lokacin ƙuruciya" - ya halarci gasar Olympics a shekara ta 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu sanadiyyar ciwon daji bayan shekara uku - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wanda ya fuskanci irin waɗannan matsalolin.
Ma'auratan sun haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley a watan Yuni, kuma Daley ya ce "hankalinsa" ya canja.
Ya ce: "Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, zan ce, 'Ina bukatar in ci lambar zinariya.'
"A gaskiya, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinariya muhimmanci.
Robbie ne zan lashe lambar zinariya a gasar Olympics".
An ba wa ɗanta sunan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana ɗan shekara 40 bayan an gano cewa yana da ciwon daji a kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa zai mutu ba kuma ya ce ɗaya daga cikin abubuwan da ya yi tambaya a ƙarshe shi ne ko suna da tikiti na zuwa birnin Landan a shekara ta 2012 - domin yana so ya kasance a jere da wuri.
"Ba zan iya cewa Baba, ba za ka iya kasancewa a jere na farko ba", in ji ta.
"Sa'ad da ta daina numfashi, na riƙe ta a hannuna, kuma bayan ta daina numfashi kuma ta mutu ne na fahimci cewa ba ta da wata matsala", in ji ta.
A shekara ta 2012, Daley ta yi tsere a gasar Olympics kuma ta lashe tagulla.
Ta ce: "Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da nake so a dukan rayuwata - yin tsalle a gaban 'yan'uwana a Wasannin Olympics, na ji daɗin hakan sosai.
Wannan ya motsa waƙar da ta fi so - Proud by Heather Small - wadda ta motsa shi sa'ad da yake shirin gasar Olympics kuma ta sa ya ci gaba da yin sanyin gwiwa.
