Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
A ranar Jumma'a, wata girgizar ƙasa da tsunami ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 384 a birnin Palu da ke ƙasar Indonisiya.
Da yake babu hanyar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su san abin da ke faruwa a Donggala ba, da ke arewacin Palu kuma kusa da inda girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta faru.
Mutane fiye da 16,000 ne aka kwashe daga Palu bayan wannan guguwar.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne kuma a shekara ta 2017, mazaunan birnin sun kai 379,800.
A lokacin ne girgizar ƙasar da tsunami suka auku a birnin.
Donggala yana kusa da gaɓar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi kuma yana da nisan mil 300.
A shekara ta 2017, mazaunan wannan yanki sun kai 299,200.
Kamfanonin kamun kifi da noma ne suka fi taimaka wa tattalin arziki a yankin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donngala da ke bakin teku.
Ana kuma hakar ma'adanai da ake kira Nickel a lardin, amma an fi yin hakan a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Agaji ta ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi tsunami a Palu da Donngala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, wata guguwar tsunami ta sake aukuwa a yammacin Donggala, kuma ta kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa kuma hakan yana faruwa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami da suka auku a wannan yankin a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 9 da ɗigo 9 ta afku a yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonisiya kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a bakin tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa da yawa a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen watan Maris da kuma farkon watan Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke kusa da Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin Yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra kuma hakan ya haddasa tsunami mai tsawon mita 10.
2016: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin gaske ta auku a yankin Pidie Jaya da ke kudancin Aceh, kuma ta halaka abubuwa da yawa.
