A shekara ta 1953 ne aka kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a New York, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an tuhume su da yin leƙen asiri ga ƙasar Soviet a lokacin Yaƙin Cacar Baki shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe iyalin Rosenberg da kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
