Masana sun ce ana jin zafin yakin kasuwanci tsakanin Amirka da China, kuma da yake ba za a daina yaƙin nan da nan ba, hakan zai iya amfanar Beijing a nan gaba.
Shugaban Amurka, Donald Trump, ya ba da gargaɗi na farko a farkon wannan bazarar lokacin da ya ɗora haraji kan manyan kayayyakin China da suka haɗa da hasken rana, ƙarfe, da aluminum.
An saka ƙarin haraji a kan kayayyaki da suka kai dala biliyan 200 (dala biliyan 200), wato, rabin kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su Amirka daga ƙasar Sin.
A kwanan nan, Beijing ta biya harajin da ya kai kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa ɗari a kan kayayyakin Amirka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta yi gasa da Amurka, kuma wannan ƙasa ta biyu mafi arziki a duniya ba za ta yi watsi da hakan ba.
Idan Washington ta janye daga wannan yaki, hakan zai nuna cewa ta amince da shawarwarin da China ta bayar, amma idan China ta mika wuya ga Amurka, hakan zai zama abin takaici ga shugaban kasar Sin, Xi Jinping.
Amma, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi amfani da katunan da ta samu, za a iya samun ci gaba a cinikin da ake yi da Amirka kuma hakan zai sa ƙasar Sin ta daina dogaro da juna.
Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike a kan harkokin Asiya a wata cibiyar bincike da ke Amirka ta ce: "Hukumar Washington da Beijing suna iya sa tattalin arzikin waɗannan ƙasashe ya yi sanyi fiye da yadda mutane suke zato.
Ministan Harkokin Waje ya ce Siriya ta shirya ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijira da ke dawowa
Siriya ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijirar da suka zaɓi su dawo kuma ta nemi taimako don sake gina ƙasar da yaƙi ya halaka fiye da shekara bakwai.
Sa'ad da yake jawabi a Babban Taron Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya, ministan harkokin waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin ƙasar yana daɗa kyau.
Ya ce: Yanzu yanayin ya kasance da kwanciyar hankali kuma babu tsoro, saboda ci gaba da aka samu wajen yaƙi da ta'addanci.
Gwamnati tana ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka halaka don a dawo da rayuwa.
Yanzu yanayin ya yi kyau don 'yan gudun hijira su koma ƙasarsu da suka tsere daga ta'addanci da kuma matsalar tattalin arziki da ke sa su wahalar biyan bukatun iyalansu.
Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya ta kimanta cewa mutane miliyan 5.5 ne suka gudu daga ƙasar Siriya tun daga lokacin da aka soma yaƙi a shekara ta 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suka rage a ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Siriya za ta yi godiya don taimakon da aka yi don a sake gina ƙasar.
Amma ya nanata cewa ba za su karɓi taimako na musamman daga ƙasashen da suke goyon bayan tawaye ba.
Turai ta ci kofin Ryder Cup a birnin Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 lokacin da ta doke Team USA ta hanyar zira kwallaye 16.5 yayin da Amurka ta zira 10.5, lokacin da suke wasa a Le Golf National a kusa da Paris, Faransa.
A yanzu haka, an ci Amurka a Turai sau shida a jere, kuma a ƙarshe ta ci gasar Ryder a Turai a shekara ta 1993.
Ƙasar Turai ta ci gaba da yin nasara sa'ad da Thomas Bjorn, shugaban tawagar Denmark, ya ci maki 14.5 da ake bukata don ya ci Amirka.
Phil Mickelson, dan wasan Amurka, ya gama wasan yana buga kwallo a baya don ya jefa kwallonsa ta farko a cikin ruwa a rami na 3 a rami na 16, don haka ya rasa Francesco Molinari.
Wannan ɗan ƙasar Italiya ne ya fi kowacce 'yar wasa yin nasara a wannan wasan, kuma shi ne ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka soma wannan wasan a shekara ta 1979.
Jordan Spieth na Amirka ya yi nasara a kan ɗan wasa na Ƙasar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasa mafi kyau a duniya, Dustin Johnson, Ian Poulter na Ingila ya ci shi 2 da 1, wanda wataƙila shi ne ya yi wasa na ƙarshe a gasar Ryder.
Sergio Garcia na Spain, wanda ya ci kofin Ryder sau takwas, shi ne ɗan wasa da ya fi cin kofin Turai da yawa kuma yana da maki 25.5.
Ba na yawan kuka, amma a yau ba na iya kame kaina.
Kuma lokacin rani yana da wuya.
Na gode wa Thomas don ya ɗauke ni kuma ya nuna mini cewa ya amince da ni.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da na sake samun wannan kofin.
"Su ne tawagar da ta yi nasara, kuma ina alfahari da cewa na yi wani abu a wannan nasarar", in ji Garcia, wanda ya damu da nasarar Turai.
Ya ba da wutar ga abokin aikinsa John Ram wanda ya ci Tiger Woods, zakaran golf na Amurka, 2&1 a ranar Lahadi a wasan mutum daya.
Rahm, ɗan shekara 23, ya ce: "Ina alfahari sosai da na ci Tiger Woods, na yi farin cikin kallon wasanninsa.
Woods ya ci duka wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wannan shi ne babban ci gaba da wani ɗan wasa ya samu, ya ci kofin 14 kuma shi ne na biyu bayan Jack Nicklaus.
Ƙungiyar golf ta Amirka tana da matsayi mai kyau a wannan makon, amma ba su da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas, da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasan golf mai kyau a waɗannan wasannin.
Kyaftin din tawagar Amurka, Jim Furyk, ya yi magana bayan wasan da tawagarsa ta yi, ya ce, "Ina alfahari da waɗannan mutane, sun yi gwagwarmaya.
A wannan safiya mun yi wasa da tawagar Turai.
Mun yi ƙoƙari.
Mun yi wa Thomas gaisuwa.
Shi kyaftin ne mai ƙwazo.
Dukan 'yan wasansa 12 suna wasa sosai.
Za mu sake tsara kanmu, zan yi aiki tare da PGA na Amurka da Kwamitin Ryder Cup kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan 'yan'uwa 12 kuma ina farin cikin yin aiki tare da su.
Ya kamata mu daraja su.
Wasan ya sa mu baƙin ciki.
Bayani na Kwanan nan Game da Ruwan Tekun da ke Ruwa A Pinellas, Manatee, da Sarasota
Wani rahoto na kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobin daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa yawan gurɓataccen ruwan teku ya ragu a yankunan da ke kusa da Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an ba da rahoton cewa a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte, da Collier an ga wasu tasoshin ruwa a cikin teku , wanda ke nuna cewa gurɓatawar tana raguwa.
An kiyasta cewa yankin da ake gurɓata ruwan teku yana da nisan mil 130 daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudu na Lee.
An gano wasu kwalabe da ke ɗauke da balaguro a kusan mil 10 daga bakin tekun Hillsborough County da kuma wasu wurare a makon da ya shige.
An sake gano gurɓataccen ruwan teku a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an ba da rahoton cewa an gano tsaka-tsakin gurɓataccen yanayi a bakin tekun Pinellas County, mafi ƙanƙanci zuwa mafi girma a kusa da Hillsborough County, mafi ƙanƙanta zuwa mafi girma a Manatee County, mafi ƙanƙanta zuwa mafi girma a bakin tekun Sarasota County, mafi ƙanƙanta zuwa mafi girma a Charlotte County, mafi ƙanƙanta zuwa mafi girma a bakin tekun Lee County, da mafi ƙanƙanta a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun ciwon numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier.
Ba a samu rahoton ciwon numfashi a Arewa maso Yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
